{"type": "article", "id": 13051, "title": "Porsche Design & RIMOWA 旅行箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-05T07:00:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122456c8bn973w2FURHkhy.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tPorsche Design 最近和德国旅行箱制造商 RIMOWA 合作推出了 “RS 2.7” PTS 联名旅行箱系列，设计灵感来自 1973 年推出的 Porsche 911 Carrera RS 2.7 跑车，用白绿配色致敬经典跑车。材料上，这款旅行箱采用 PTS 轻量聚碳酸酯作为外壳，目前有一大一小两种尺寸，分别售价 1190 和 950 美元，这是<a href=\"http://shop3.porsche.com/usa/specials/rs/wap0354010gyxx/pts-ultralight-luggage-m-rs-2-7-limited-edition.pdds\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140704Yn5XKMsCbP6dwrhJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140705o79gTGhAquieyBYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}